title: Thanksgiving NFL Games Recap Podcast (Football 11/23)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner-McGough and R.J. White to break down the three Thanksgiving games. The guys break down Redskins-Cowboys (2:00), Falcons-Saints (16:45) and Bears-Lions (30:15).
